name: CI Utilities Giants Covered Call ETF
longDescription: The ETF's investment objective is to provide Unitholders, through an actively managed portfolio. The issuers included in the portfolio, which are based on their market capitalization, may be adjusted based on the Portfolio Managers view on the liquidity of the issuers equity securities and their related call options.
